  "threads": [
    {
      "n": "01",
      "h": "Analyst by habit",
      "p": "I tend to read the pattern in the data first, then build the fix. It's the habit under most of what I do."
    },
    {
      "n": "02",
      "h": "Every side of the table",
      "p": "Agency, brand, retail and platform — I've been fortunate to work all four, which makes it easier to see the whole picture."
    },
    {
      "n": "03",
      "h": "Measurement first",
      "p": "From a research desk to Aleph's Google team, the constant was proving which unit of spend did the work."
    },
    {
      "n": "04",
      "h": "Constraint as craft",
      "p": "The Grand Prix came from a small-budget brief. The tighter the budget, the sharper the thinking it forces."
    }
  ],
